com.incadencecorp.coalesce.framework.iterators

Class CoalesceIterator<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.incadencecorp.coalesce.framework.iterators.CoalesceIterator<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T -
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CoalesceCodeGeneratorIterator, CoalesceIteratorDataTypes, CoalescePopulatorIterator, CoalescePrunerIterator, CoalesceUpdaterIterator, PostGreSQLRegisterIterator

    public abstract class CoalesceIterator<T>
extends Object
    This abstract class recursively iterates over an entity. If you override a visit method and return false all of its children wont be visited.
    Author:
    n78554
